main event: Three witnesses observed an unidentified flying object in L. Randolph, Tennessee on July 27, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as possibly being a drone or model aircraft., It was observed moving in a straight line at high speed for approximately 1 minute., There were no photographs or physical evidence accompanying the report., The report suggested a probable conclusion that it was a drone or model aircraft., A prior sighting of an extremely bright light at high altitude was noted in the vicinity.
